{"tid":2020563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"退出咗監警會國際專家小組嘅Clifford Stott，會自己出監警報告","createTime":"2020-05-17T07:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T07:58:34.000Z","uid":286822,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7494f412846416ef424fde85c140236e24381888","tid":2020563,"uid":286822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T07:16:32.000Z","msg":"Now IPCC report is published I am free to utilise its data as well as our own to underpin our scientific analysis of the evolution of the 2019 protest movement in Hong Kong. Hard at work over this weekend developing our report which we hope to publish on or before 9th June 2020.<br />\n<br />\n翻譯：<br />\n撐警會嘅報告出咗，我可以用報告中嘅數據，以及自己嘅數據去支持一個關於2019年香港示威運動嘅科學化分析。仲寫緊，希望可以喺6月9日前發表。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cliffordstott/status/1261699933276684288?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcliffordstott%2Fstatus%2F1261699933276684288%3Fs%3D19&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e6160IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=cb1ffdf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcliffordstott%2Fstatus%2F1261699933276684288%3Fs%3D19&h=d13b869d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cliffordstott/status/1261699933276684288?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"2c328b56c1073765c94e607d434a52764488db2d","tid":2020563,"uid":286822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T07:17:16.000Z","msg":"P牌冇得推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd89b25b37571a65eac0877380b79dc6def6d88","tid":2020563,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918bdef9f46070b399ff4e3abcf7ee21d6cde413","tid":2020563,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike